insert the following clause:</p>
         <p outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" class="- topic/p " audience="GSAR">Separate Charge for Performance Oriented
Packaging (POP) (May 2019)</p>
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li " audience="GSAR">
